06T03:12:07.000Z","msg":"推呀 推"},{"pid":"3ef4f95487ea2d9565e5f530c93e7f39a0f5bfa7","tid":1544723,"uid":83989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:12:23.000Z","msg":"美國會下周復會　舒默推動通過《香港人權與民主法案》<br />\n<br />\n美國參議院民主黨領袖舒默說，國會下星期復會後，民主黨優先推動的其中一項工作，是通過《香港人權與民主法案》。他促請參議院共和黨領袖麥康奈爾，將兩黨提出的這項法案提上議程，要求華府每年交代是否繼續賦予香港特殊待遇，包括根據1992年美國的《香港政策法》，香港在貿易和商業上享有特權。舒默發表聲明說，中國共產黨的行動，針對香港人行使言論自由和其他基本的民主權利，美方作出回應至關重要。他強調，美方必須採取行動，向中國國家主席習近平展示，美國參議院與香港人肩並肩站在一起。<br />\n<br />\n2019-09-06 10:44:20"},{"pid":"d999bf4587922b960d922836f8c70475939c0e5a","tid":1544723,"uid":41093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:12:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1421fa5dda69f31784cfeb5c2e59b2e71a3670b2","tid":1544723,"uid":19634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:12:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a4d9c97f87e822a5614b1818cbf40ee24d4256","tid":1544723,"uid":287577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:13:32.000Z","msg":"借位&amp;幫推<br />\n<br />\n（P牌都睇唔過眼) FB要人 831受害者請盡快聯絡以下團體<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545538\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545538</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"25b8e6d7be5f566aa575b9fe0cfc990afd887751","tid":1544723,"uid":302796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:13:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">老美出手前<br />\n請不要炒車</span></span>"},{"pid":"b63f4f0a1ce853bacb4f955019926387a60554f8","tid":1544723,"uid":300521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:24:23.000Z","msg":"大家9月8日去美